edu.spa.ftclib.internal.controller

Class ErrorTimeThresholdFinishingAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.spa.ftclib.internal.controller.FinishingAlgorithm
      • edu.spa.ftclib.internal.controller.ErrorTimeThresholdFinishingAlgorithm
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Finishable, Targetable, TargetableAlgorithm

    public class ErrorTimeThresholdFinishingAlgorithm
extends FinishingAlgorithm
    Uses error tolerance and time threshold to determine when to stop running the controller and count it as "finished." The robot must stay within the error tolerance continuously for the time given in the time threshold to finish.

    • Constructor Summary
